    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A polymer made from the addition polymerization of acrylonitrile. Polyacrylonitrile was first made in the late 1930s and it quickly became an important type of synthetic rubber.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
